name: STATE v. William SUNDEL et al.

parties: STATE v. William SUNDEL et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The petition for writ of certiorari is granted. The stay entered in this case on May 21, 1982 is continued until further order of this court.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Kenneth P. Madden, Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff-respondent.
Temkin & Miller, James H. Leavey, Providence, for defendant-petitioner Sundel, John A. O’Neill, Jr., Providence, for defendant-petitioner Nelson.

No. 82-220-M.P.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
July 9, 1982.
Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Kenneth P. Madden, Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff-respondent.
